1
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:34,950
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,009 --> 00:01:37,979
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:38,789 --> 00:01:40,720
I was waiting for the wrong person.

4
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,220
But she came at the right time.

5
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,620
If she hadn't come,

6
00:01:48,220 --> 00:01:49,810
I would've been dead long ago.

7
00:01:49,810 --> 00:01:50,890
Am I too stupid,

8
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:53,340
or did you not make yourself clear?

9
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:55,770
You're too stupid.

10
00:01:56,470 --> 00:01:57,800
You like her, don't you?

11
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,710
Calling it "like" would be too limiting.

12
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:05,170
So you don't like her then?

13
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:22,070
If you don't like her,
that makes things easier.

14
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:24,430
Since the Master won't let her stay
by your side,

15
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:26,030
and you won't let me kill her,

16
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:28,240
I'll just take her away. Problem solved.

17
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,710
She won't go with you.

18
00:02:31,430 --> 00:02:32,400
Don't be so sure.

19
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:35,910
With my charming good looks
and dashing style,

20
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:38,180
no beauty could possibly resist me.

21
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:40,620
Just wait and see.

22
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:02,080
Can I have this?

23
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,140
This one is already withered.

24
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,310
Its leaves

25
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,060
still show some signs of life.

26
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,560
Just as you said—

27
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,560
if someone makes an effort for it...

28
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,530
who's to say
it can't find the will to survive?

29
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,460
Imperial Physician, please hurry.

30
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:21,630
Her Highness has been coughing all night
and couldn't sleep.

31
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:22,090
Coming.

32
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:33,690
Your Highness,
the imperial physician is here.

33
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,520
This subject...

34
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:47,800
This subject pays his respects to
Your Highness.

35
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,800
That rainy night,

36
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:50,910
I failed to recognize Your Highness.

37
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,190
I deserve to die for this offense.

38
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,590
Please punish me
as Your Highness sees fit.

39
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,090
If you keep kneeling there,

40
00:03:57,450 --> 00:03:58,829
I'll never get better.

41
00:03:59,190 --> 00:03:59,920
I'm at fault.

42
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:01,860
I shall take your pulse at once.

43
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,600
Imperial Physician, please sit.

44
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,200
Thank you.

45
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:18,110
Your Highness.

46
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:33,290
How's my condition?

47
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:41,000
Your Highness's pulse is stable.

48
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,000
Nothing serious.

49
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,600
It's likely from
getting caught in the rain that day,

50
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,720
which allowed external pathogens
to invade your lungs

51
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,270
and disrupt your defensive qi.

52
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:48,750
I'll prepare some medicine

53
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,530
and have it delivered daily
for Your Highness to take.

54
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:52,659
You should recover in a couple of days.

55
00:04:52,930 --> 00:04:53,530
Thank you.

56
00:05:00,690 --> 00:05:01,620
May I ask

57
00:05:01,930 --> 00:05:03,730
your name, Imperial Physician?

58
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:05,830
My name is Xiao Tiancai.

59
00:05:08,780 --> 00:05:09,830
Tiny Genius?

60
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:11,310
Yes.

61
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,440
Your name

62
00:05:14,770 --> 00:05:15,820
is quite unique.

63
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:20,440
It's the first time anyone has said so.

64
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:23,800
Thank you for the compliment,
Your Highness.

65
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:36,240
Your Highness.

66
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,070
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

67
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:37,560
You...

68
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:38,820
What...

69
00:05:40,850 --> 00:05:41,510
Don't move!

70
00:05:46,050 --> 00:05:46,730
Bai?

71
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,800
What kind of move was that?

72
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,240
Women's self-defense technique.

73
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,159
Awesome.

74
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:52,830
That's the only move I know.

75
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,300
You all should practice hard.

76
00:05:55,350 --> 00:05:57,750
Your martial arts aren't even
as good as your mistress's.

77
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,240
Weren't you with His Majesty?

78
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,280
Why are you here?

79
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:01,090
I originally

80
00:06:01,090 --> 00:06:02,870
meant to spar with Master Bei,

81
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,860
but I couldn't find him anywhere.

82
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,840
So I had to

83
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:08,370
practice my martial arts
with them instead.

84
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:09,450
Mr. Bei?

85
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,120
He's in the backyard,

86
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:12,420
by the stone table.

87
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:17,220
Isn't there only an old maid
by the stone table?

88
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:18,780
Mr. Bei.

89
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,800
Wanyin.

90
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,770
Come on, come on.

91
00:06:20,770 --> 00:06:24,500
Look at the embroidery I made—
mandarin ducks playing on the water.

92
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,260
How is it?

93
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,930
You're "Mr. Bei"?

94
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:37,680
Why are you dressed like this?

95
00:06:39,850 --> 00:06:41,190
So you have

96
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:43,620
some secret hobbies, huh?

97
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,120
Why are you here?

98
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,670
And this embroidery of yours.

99
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:48,540
You call those mandarin ducks
playing on the water?

100
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:51,040
That's clearly a pair of chickens
flapping around.

101
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,500
Am I right, Your Highness?

102
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:55,070
Wanyin,

103
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,450
let me teach

104
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,750
this disrespectful little disciple
a lesson.

105
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,710
-Mr. Bei, I was only joking.
-Go.

106
00:07:09,990 --> 00:07:11,450
Not the face! Not the face!

107
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,870
Why were you being so sarcastic?

108
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:31,330
Just

109
00:07:32,230 --> 00:07:33,630
trying to make you smile.

110
00:07:37,210 --> 00:07:37,620
Bai.

111
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:40,360
You've been roaming the world
for so many years.

112
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,940
You must have been to many places, right?

113
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:42,890
Of course.

114
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:46,690
I've seen sunsets over long rivers,
clouds over high mountains,

115
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:48,830
thousand-year-old temples,
and beacon towers stretching for miles.

116
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,950
Your Highness, just name a place.

117
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:52,480
Let's see if there's anywhere
I haven't been.

118
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,640
I envy you so much.

119
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,470
What about you, Your Highness?

120
00:07:58,470 --> 00:07:59,600
Where have you been?

121
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:02,630
I...

122
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:11,810
Apart from Zhaoyang Palace,
I've only been to Yongyan Hall

123
00:08:11,810 --> 00:08:13,210
and the Imperial Garden.

124
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:17,310
I don't think I've been outside the palace

125
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,900
since entering it.

126
00:08:21,170 --> 00:08:22,430
That's so boring.

127
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:27,650
A spirited beauty like you

128
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:29,550
shouldn't be confined here.

129
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:31,340
Why not come with me?

130
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:34,690
I'll take you to see mountains and waters,
to chase sunsets.

131
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:35,770
Right now?

132
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,980
Your Highness,

133
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,400
the world outside

134
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,559
is not only beautiful

135
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,440
but also full of the unknown.

136
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,010
I once encountered wild men

137
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,510
in the dense forests of the Southwest.

138
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:49,510
And on a small island in the East Sea,

139
00:08:49,540 --> 00:08:51,070
I came across giant beasts.

140
00:08:51,660 --> 00:08:53,320
Another time, passing through Wuling,

141
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,030
I followed a stream into a cave,

142
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:56,000
and when I came out,

143
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,470
I found a village hidden

144
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,020
among flower-covered mountains.

145
00:08:59,020 --> 00:08:59,750
It was full of people

146
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:02,610
who had been isolated from the world
for centuries.

147
00:09:03,590 --> 00:09:05,190
"The Peach Blossom Spring"?

148
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:08,870
How did you know
those flowers were peach blossoms?

149
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,560
Well...

150
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:11,540
Anyway, when the wind blew,

151
00:09:11,670 --> 00:09:13,530
petals fell everywhere

152
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:14,940
like pink snow.

153
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,630
I'll never forget

154
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,300
that sight for the rest of my life.

155
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:21,540
If I ever get the chance,

156
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,340
I'd really love to see it myself.

157
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:25,610
Wuling is far away,

158
00:09:26,050 --> 00:09:27,850
but I can show it to you right now.

159
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:34,260
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

160
00:09:34,470 --> 00:09:35,690
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

161
00:09:36,070 --> 00:09:38,220
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

162
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:40,000
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

163
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,360
♪ Words unspoken ♪

164
00:09:43,970 --> 00:09:46,340
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

165
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:50,270
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

166
00:09:50,570 --> 00:09:51,610
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

167
00:09:52,110 --> 00:09:54,070
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

168
00:09:54,590 --> 00:09:55,940
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

169
00:09:56,050 --> 00:09:58,460
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

170
00:10:00,050 --> 00:10:03,490
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

171
00:10:03,990 --> 00:10:07,250
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

172
00:10:08,050 --> 00:10:10,980
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

173
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:13,310
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

174
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,080
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

175
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:17,130
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

176
00:10:17,430 --> 00:10:19,530
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

177
00:10:20,010 --> 00:10:23,160
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

178
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:26,310
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

179
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:27,520
♪ Still unchanged ♪

180
00:10:27,990 --> 00:10:30,800
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

181
00:10:31,450 --> 00:10:32,900
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

182
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:37,390
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

183
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:55,440
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

184
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,480
Why are you here?

185
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:58,930
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

186
00:10:57,470 --> 00:10:58,800
To have dinner with you.

187
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:01,370
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

188
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:03,160
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

189
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:05,180
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

190
00:11:05,450 --> 00:11:07,560
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

191
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:11,210
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

192
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:14,390
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

193
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,090
All the effort, down the drain.

194
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,560
♪ Still unchanged ♪

195
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:18,930
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

196
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,860
Don't move.

197
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,930
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

198
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:28,340
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

199
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:39,150
All of you, leave.

200
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:51,030
Then I'll just dig in.

201
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:51,560
Go ahead.

202
00:11:54,130 --> 00:11:55,220
Smells so good!

203
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,810
Get me a bowl and chopsticks, will you?

204
00:11:57,810 --> 00:11:58,860
Imperial Guards!

205
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,130
Don't call them.

206
00:12:00,810 --> 00:12:02,000
I won't be freeloading.

207
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,930
I'll give you intelligence on Yan State
in exchange.

208
00:12:05,170 --> 00:12:05,780
Deal?

209
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:12,610
Situated between grasslands and desert,

210
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:15,790
they live at nature's mercy
and love causing trouble.

211
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:17,910
They pillage, burn, and plunder—

212
00:12:17,930 --> 00:12:21,430
strong in body but lacking honor.

213
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:23,650
What I'm talking about

214
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:25,630
[Yan] [Stealing]

215
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,440
is the Yan State.

216
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,790
They don't just steal food, horses,
and cloth—

217
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:32,520
[Yan] [Stealing] [Xia]

218
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:29,550
they even...

219
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,510
want to take over

220
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:32,610
our entire Xia.

221
00:12:36,060 --> 00:12:37,150
I'd like to ask

222
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,680
about the royal family of Yan State.

223
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:47,150
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]

224
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,820
Zhaluowahan is the emperor of Yan,

225
00:12:44,250 --> 00:12:46,680
cunning and deceitful behind his smile.

226
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:53,130
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]
[Prince Tu'er]

227
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,910
Prince Tu'er is busy on the battlefield,

228
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:51,970
proud of his talent

229
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,360
to the point of arrogance.

230
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,960
Your Highness, please look.

231
00:12:57,380 --> 00:13:00,180
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]

232
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,610
They're uncle and nephew,

233
00:12:59,830 --> 00:13:00,990
but actually rivals.

234
00:13:00,180 --> 00:13:01,010
[Prince Tu'er]

235
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:02,710
Apart from both hating our empire,

236
00:13:02,710 --> 00:13:05,040
they can't see eye to eye
on anything else.

237
00:13:06,650 --> 00:13:07,860
Between these two,

238
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,410
who would be easier to turn?

239
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:13,200
Actually, neither is very likely.

240
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,270
The Emperor of Yan lost an eye
to our arrow.

241
00:13:15,270 --> 00:13:16,200
As for Tu'er...

242
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,110
he has some

243
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,300
old grievances with His Majesty.

244
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:21,520
Grievances?

245
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,870
What grievances?

246
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,630
Should I

247
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,050
not have brought up...

248
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:32,150
Beautiful Lady Shanyi?

249
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,080
Your Highness, please look.

250
00:13:39,140 --> 00:13:40,740
Beautiful Lady Shanyi?

251
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:42,840
Who is she?

252
00:13:42,860 --> 00:13:44,660
Tu'er's childhood sweetheart.

253
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:48,340
Years ago, the Emperor of Yan sent her
to dance in the palace,

254
00:13:48,340 --> 00:13:50,000
where she caused quite a stir.

255
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:50,480
Later,

256
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,410
she was granted the title of
Beautiful Lady.

257
00:13:53,410 --> 00:13:54,470
But not long after,

258
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,780
[Beautiful Lady Shanyi]

259
00:13:54,730 --> 00:13:56,480
she was accused of attempting to
assassinate the Emperor

260
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:58,490
under the pretext of
attending the bedchamber

261
00:13:58,490 --> 00:13:59,530
and was executed.

262
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,600
Yan State used this as an excuse

263
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,800
to declare war on Xia,

264
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,510
fighting for many years.

265
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,910
I didn't know about this.

266
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,010
Then...

267
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:11,070
how do you know all this?

268
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:12,600
No matter what,

269
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,920
we should send someone
to talk with them separately.

270
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,790
Peace negotiations are crucial
for our nation.

271
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:17,720
If either of them

272
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,190
is a wise ruler,

273
00:14:20,090 --> 00:14:22,600
they should know to set aside
personal grudges.

274
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,060
Wanyin,

275
00:14:24,130 --> 00:14:24,990
who do you think

276
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:26,750
would be suitable to send?

277
00:14:30,130 --> 00:14:33,720
Among the scholars, the one skilled in
diplomacy and fluent in the Yan language

278
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,770
is Wang Zhao.

279
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:37,210
Gentlemen.

280
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:40,030
Look.

281
00:14:40,390 --> 00:14:40,840
Wang,

282
00:14:40,950 --> 00:14:42,800
I must say, in this outfit,

283
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:45,030
you really do look a bit like
someone from Yan State.

284
00:14:45,030 --> 00:14:45,600
Well?

285
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:46,870
I wore this specially tonight

286
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:48,210
to show all of you first!

287
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,440
Come on, sit, sit!

288
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:51,650
Where is Er Lan?

289
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,610
Why isn't he here?

290
00:14:52,610 --> 00:14:53,370
Er Lan...

291
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:54,840
Tonight...

292
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:57,360
the Minister of Revenue is
hosting a banquet.

293
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:57,890
Er Lan...

294
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,440
He...

295
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:03,030
accepted the invitation and went.

296
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:04,570
Isn't he just socializing on your behalf?

297
00:15:04,570 --> 00:15:06,050
-What do you mean...
-Er

298
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,350
asked me to bring you some money.

299
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:09,900
-For the road...
-I can't take it.

300
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,600
His Majesty has already allocated funds.

301
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,640
Why be polite?

302
00:15:12,990 --> 00:15:14,030
It's not my money anyway.

303
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:15,360
He sent money to him too?

304
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:17,030
What?

305
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:19,690
You also brought some money for him?

306
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:22,550
Wang,

307
00:15:22,910 --> 00:15:23,870
travel rich even if you live poor.

308
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:24,870
Take this as well.

309
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,350
Thank you, Li.

310
00:15:27,690 --> 00:15:29,750
You talk the most—what did you bring?

311
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,200
Here.

312
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:34,030
I personally went to Nanshan Temple

313
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:35,120
to pray and obtain this for you.

314
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,000
When traveling far from home,

315
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,120
ability is one thing,

316
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,920
but luck is also very important!

317
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:39,420
Come on!

318
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:40,040
Put it on!

319
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:40,630
Okay!

320
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:43,350
It's been blessed by a high monk.

321
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,100
I found a copy

322
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:48,350
of "The Gazetteer of Yan" for you, Wang.

323
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,950
It contains information about
Yan State's customs and culture.

324
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:51,240
[The Gazetteer of Yan]

325
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,620
I hope it'll be of help.

326
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:53,580
Cen,

327
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:56,520
that's very thoughtful of you.

328
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,120
What's

329
00:15:57,620 --> 00:15:58,800
this flower?

330
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:00,440
I've never seen it before.

331
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,200
Camel Bell.

332
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,030
Camel Bell?

333
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:04,470
That's right.

334
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:06,920
It's a plant unique to Yan State.

335
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,240
Legend has it

336
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,790
that it grew from the tears of camels
who couldn't

337
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:12,440
bear to part with their beloved.

338
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,470
The people of Yan believe

339
00:16:13,470 --> 00:16:15,390
that those who travel with this flower

340
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:16,790
will eventually reunite

341
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,620
with their loved ones.

342
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,060
If that's so,

343
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:27,680
with this flower, Wang,

344
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,680
you'll surely

345
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,460
return safe and sound!

346
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,300
Indeed.

347
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,840
The journey ahead

348
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:35,120
is long and fraught with difficulties.

349
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:35,550
Let us

350
00:16:35,970 --> 00:16:37,720
offer this humble cup of wine

351
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,760
to wish you a safe journey, Wang.

352
00:16:43,410 --> 00:16:44,560
May we encourage

353
00:16:45,770 --> 00:16:46,500
one another.

354
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:57,840
[General Luo, things in the palace
have been peaceful recently.]

355
00:16:57,840 --> 00:17:00,880
[I'm trying to save your son.
You may rest assured.]

356
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:03,130
Your Highness,

357
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:05,200
there's news from the palace.

358
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,030
That mysterious martial arts master

359
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:08,359
at the Emperor's side has appeared again.

360
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,589
Where?

361
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:15,079
Zhaoyang Palace.

362
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:16,810
Zhaoyang Palace?

363
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:23,990
It seems it's time

364
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:26,880
for me to have a chat

365
00:17:27,859 --> 00:17:28,790
with Consort Yu.

366
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,360
This commoner, Wang Zhao,

367
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,420
pays his respects to Your Majesty...

368
00:17:53,110 --> 00:17:55,070
There are too many eyes and ears around.

369
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:57,480
Don't bother with
such formalities, Mr. Wang.

370
00:17:57,480 --> 00:18:00,260
To avoid the eyes and ears of
Prince Duan and the Empress Dowager,

371
00:18:00,260 --> 00:18:02,170
you must disguise yourself as a merchant

372
00:18:02,170 --> 00:18:03,460
and travel to Yan State.

373
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:05,890
I can't give you an official decree
for this journey

374
00:18:05,890 --> 00:18:07,220
nor a legitimate cause.

375
00:18:08,290 --> 00:18:09,960
I can't send guards with you,

376
00:18:10,370 --> 00:18:11,670
only a few secret ones

377
00:18:12,770 --> 00:18:14,300
to protect you discreetly.

378
00:18:15,090 --> 00:18:16,490
Once you reach Yan State,

379
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:17,870
you'll also need to

380
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:19,790
play it by ear.

381
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:22,230
The journey ahead is long

382
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,490
and extremely dangerous.

383
00:18:25,300 --> 00:18:26,310
I hope you will...

384
00:18:27,970 --> 00:18:30,030
take good care of yourself, Mr. Wang.

385
00:18:33,410 --> 00:18:34,810
Thank you, Your Majesty.

386
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,240
This commoner...

387
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:43,340
This commoner lost his father
at a young age.

388
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,700
My only concern

389
00:18:45,630 --> 00:18:47,000
is my widowed mother at home.

390
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,930
I'll take good care of your mother.

391
00:18:49,950 --> 00:18:51,750
You go for the sake of the nation.

392
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:52,820
I...

393
00:18:54,350 --> 00:18:56,220
will certainly take care of everything

394
00:18:56,220 --> 00:18:58,150
so you have nothing to worry about.

395
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:01,860
I will do my utmost

396
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:03,930
to stop the war and establish trade.

397
00:19:03,930 --> 00:19:04,730
I won't return

398
00:19:06,260 --> 00:19:07,190
until I succeed.

399
00:19:12,140 --> 00:19:13,940
We are counting on you, Mr. Wang.

400
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:53,300
[Camel Bell]

401
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:01,960
My Lady!

402
00:20:02,770 --> 00:20:04,270
Just now, an unfamiliar young eunuch

403
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,320
shoved this into my hands.

404
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:06,610
When I called out to him, he ran away,

405
00:20:06,610 --> 00:20:08,410
and I couldn't catch up with him.

406
00:20:16,450 --> 00:20:19,720
A kindred spirit is hard to find—
why hesitate?

407
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:22,100
Let's meet at the flower house today.

408
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,010
You may leave first.

409
00:20:26,270 --> 00:20:26,940
Yes.

410
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,640
Prince Duan, you were in such a hurry
to see me.

411
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:00,300
-What's...
-Wanyin, have you

412
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,700
seen anything lately?

413
00:21:02,890 --> 00:21:03,590
Seen?

414
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:09,270
Didn't you tell me before

415
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:13,100
that you could use foresight
to predict the future?

416
00:21:15,360 --> 00:21:16,040
Yes.

417
00:21:17,050 --> 00:21:18,010
I have...

418
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:20,360
indeed seen some things lately.

419
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:23,270
Like what?

420
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:25,370
Like,

421
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:28,850
in the dense forests of the Southwest,

422
00:21:29,050 --> 00:21:31,180
footprints of wild men have appeared.

423
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,430
And

424
00:21:32,980 --> 00:21:35,670
on a small island in East Lake,

425
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:39,400
there seem to be giants
swimming in the inner lake.

426
00:21:40,580 --> 00:21:42,670
Following the stream
toward the mountains in Wuling,

427
00:21:42,670 --> 00:21:43,780
I saw light ahead.

428
00:21:44,150 --> 00:21:46,850
Beyond the mountain are hillsides
covered with peach trees.

429
00:21:46,850 --> 00:21:48,000
I've heard

430
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:52,130
that the martial arts master
by the Emperor's side has appeared again—

431
00:21:52,370 --> 00:21:54,290
and this time, inside the palace.

432
00:21:56,250 --> 00:21:57,780
He has discovered Bei Zhou?

433
00:21:58,790 --> 00:22:00,920
It's very dangerous
if we don't eliminate this guy.

434
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,510
Can you help me foresee

435
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,180
how we can get rid of him?

436
00:22:05,690 --> 00:22:07,420
Is this information reliable?

437
00:22:07,910 --> 00:22:09,770
How did Your Highness learn of it?

438
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,040
I saw it in my dream

439
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:17,090
using my foresight as well.

440
00:22:19,950 --> 00:22:22,020
You just said you "heard" about it.

441
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,960
You bastard—

442
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:26,470
lying without even
preparing your story properly.

443
00:22:26,470 --> 00:22:29,270
Is that Imperial Physician Xiao
competent or not?

444
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:31,130
When others are sick,
the physicians tell them to stay in bed,

445
00:22:31,130 --> 00:22:32,860
yet he encourages you to go out.

446
00:22:34,810 --> 00:22:36,210
The sunshine is perfect.

447
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:38,270
Some moderate sun exposure

448
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:39,870
is beneficial for recovery.

449
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:43,580
Still, there's no need to come all the way
to the flower house.

450
00:22:43,580 --> 00:22:45,550
I dropped an earring when I was sheltering
from the rain the other day.

451
00:22:45,550 --> 00:22:46,880
It might be somewhere in the flower house.

452
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,010
Let's go look for it.

453
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:50,540
My Lady,

454
00:22:50,700 --> 00:22:52,310
isn't that Prince Duan and...

455
00:22:52,310 --> 00:22:53,670
Why are they together?

456
00:23:02,660 --> 00:23:03,190
Wanyin.

457
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,340
Are you willing to help me?

458
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:09,580
Prince Duan, please wait a moment.

459
00:23:09,580 --> 00:23:10,640
Let me give it a try.

460
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:17,810
Now both Bei Zhou and Bai are
in the palace,

461
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:20,520
yet he only knows of one master,

462
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:22,210
not two.

463
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,410
I saw...

464
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:35,820
what seemed to be a tall man

465
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:38,040
appearing in a corridor.

466
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,000
A corridor?

467
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:48,740
Which...

468
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:51,390
corridor?

469
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:53,130
It seemed to be in the Imperial Garden,

470
00:23:53,130 --> 00:23:54,190
but I can't be sure.

471
00:23:55,110 --> 00:23:57,270
It was too rushed to see clearly.

472
00:23:57,810 --> 00:24:00,100
Have you consulted Consort Xie about it?

473
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:04,520
I came to you first.

474
00:24:06,910 --> 00:24:09,240
If you can't foresee it within three days,

475
00:24:10,740 --> 00:24:13,300
it won't be too late for me
to ask her then.

476
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:16,390
Who leaked the information?

477
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:19,120
Could it be...

478
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:20,820
Just now, an unfamiliar young eunuch

479
00:24:20,820 --> 00:24:22,020
shoved this into my hands.

480
00:24:22,020 --> 00:24:23,200
When I called out to him, he ran away,

481
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:25,000
and I couldn't catch up with him.

482
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:25,850
My Lady.

483
00:24:27,410 --> 00:24:28,820
This isn't the way back to the palace.

484
00:24:28,820 --> 00:24:31,150
I saw you walking this way
with your head down,

485
00:24:31,150 --> 00:24:32,750
so I didn't dare disturb you.

486
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,510
My Lady,

487
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:42,270
this is flower tea I prepared myself

488
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:44,030
to clear internal heat and detoxify.

489
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,360
Would you like to try it?

490
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:47,030
No need.

491
00:24:48,310 --> 00:24:50,070
My Lady, you've been looking worried

492
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:51,470
ever since you returned.

493
00:24:52,830 --> 00:24:54,430
Is something troubling you?

494
00:24:58,550 --> 00:24:59,920
I just saw Prince Duan,

495
00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:03,100
who apparently offended His Majesty

496
00:25:03,790 --> 00:25:05,190
and was about to be caned.

497
00:25:05,930 --> 00:25:09,190
I overheard His Majesty
instructing the secret guards...

498
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:12,470
to be especially brutal
during the punishment.

499
00:25:12,570 --> 00:25:13,830
I wonder if Prince Duan

500
00:25:15,010 --> 00:25:16,080
will survive this.

501
00:25:16,980 --> 00:25:18,240
How could this happen?

502
00:25:19,990 --> 00:25:21,590
Should I go ask around?

503
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:22,650
Are you insane?

504
00:25:23,020 --> 00:25:24,620
If His Majesty catches you at this time,

505
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:26,680
how am I supposed to explain it to him?

506
00:25:28,090 --> 00:25:30,020
I didn't think it through, My Lady.

507
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:35,000
You may leave now.

508
00:25:45,750 --> 00:25:46,590
Let go of me!

509
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,390
Let go of me!

510
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:49,540
Kneel!

511
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:53,310
Your Highness is most perceptive.

512
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:54,400
This maid snuck out

513
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:56,240
to pass information to a eunuch

514
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:57,240
bribed by Prince Duan.

515
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,590
We apprehended her on the spot.

516
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,570
You're lying!

517
00:25:59,930 --> 00:26:00,640
My Lady.

518
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,850
When did you start
consorting with Prince Duan?

519
00:26:02,850 --> 00:26:04,320
I didn't!

520
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:07,510
How could I ever dare harbor such thoughts
toward His Highness?

521
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:08,510
Still denying it?

522
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:11,750
My Lady,

523
00:26:12,790 --> 00:26:14,510
I was worried
you were concerned about His Highness,

524
00:26:14,510 --> 00:26:16,310
so I went out to find a way to help.

525
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:17,440
My Lady,

526
00:26:18,270 --> 00:26:20,260
how can you not trust me?

527
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:24,130
It's because I trusted you too much

528
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:27,010
that I gave you the chance to betray me.

529
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:29,150
I've never betrayed you,

530
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,550
and my loyalty has never wavered.

531
00:26:32,650 --> 00:26:33,510
Tell the truth!

532
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:37,800
It was the Lantern Festival—

533
00:26:38,060 --> 00:26:40,990
the Lantern Festival
before you entered the palace.

534
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:47,900
I was by your side then,

535
00:26:49,470 --> 00:26:51,270
when you first met His Highness.

536
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:55,580
I watched the two of you
fall for each other.

537
00:26:57,590 --> 00:26:59,940
You were so happy back then.

538
00:27:02,330 --> 00:27:04,330
After entering the palace with you,

539
00:27:04,890 --> 00:27:07,420
he occasionally came to chat with me.

540
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:08,530
That's all.

541
00:27:18,610 --> 00:27:20,070
So you've been passing information
about me

542
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:21,400
to him all along?

543
00:27:23,130 --> 00:27:24,730
I just don't understand...

544
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:29,270
why you didn't choose His Highness

545
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:31,000
but chose that tyrant instead.

546
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:35,650
You used to despise the tyrant.

547
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:39,100
You cried every day and couldn't eat.

548
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:42,630
But ever since you suddenly started
attending the tyrant at night,

549
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:44,030
everything has changed.

550
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:47,020
I understand even less

551
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:49,330
why you've clearly fallen for the tyrant

552
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:51,780
yet still string Prince Duan along,

553
00:27:52,930 --> 00:27:55,390
letting him waste away for you
day after day,

554
00:27:56,460 --> 00:27:59,860
while you only care about
enjoying yourself with the tyrant.

555
00:28:02,750 --> 00:28:04,950
So the day I left the palace in disguise—

556
00:28:05,670 --> 00:28:07,670
it was also you who told Prince Duan?

557
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:08,690
It was me.

558
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:15,440
But that day, Master Yu had just been
framed by Consort Shu's family,

559
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:18,410
and then His Majesty immediately took you
out of the palace.

560
00:28:18,410 --> 00:28:20,320
I was worried about your safety.

561
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:25,950
It just so happened
that His Highness sent someone to ask,

562
00:28:26,460 --> 00:28:27,640
so I told them

563
00:28:27,670 --> 00:28:29,560
which gate you left from.

564
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:35,200
Your Highness,

565
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:36,200
shall we kill her?

566
00:28:40,110 --> 00:28:41,130
My Lady...

567
00:28:42,430 --> 00:28:43,220
My Lady!

568
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:48,110
I entered your household at age five

569
00:28:48,210 --> 00:28:49,420
to serve you.

570
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:53,740
We ate and slept together,
and I cared about everything about you.

571
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:56,700
You must believe I would never harm you.

572
00:28:57,090 --> 00:28:59,820
Everything I did was for your sake,

573
00:28:59,850 --> 00:29:00,880
My Lady.

574
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:29,960
Take her back and lock her up.

575
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:33,290
Without my permission,

576
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:35,240
don't let her out.

577
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:36,070
My Lady!

578
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:37,240
My Lady...

579
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:40,620
The tyrant demoted Master Yu
and neglected you!

580
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:43,440
My Lady, you need to come to your senses!

581
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:49,110
I've just returned to the palace

582
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:51,710
and heard about what happened with Mei.

583
00:30:52,750 --> 00:30:53,680
Are you alright?

584
00:31:04,850 --> 00:31:06,710
I've been thinking for a long time

585
00:31:06,780 --> 00:31:07,980
and just remembered.

586
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:13,590
In the novel, the original female lead
lost her mother at a young age

587
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:15,320
and grew up without affection.

588
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:16,890
When she was eight,

589
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:20,480
she caught highly contagious measles.

590
00:31:21,470 --> 00:31:24,130
Everyone in the household
kept their distance.

591
00:31:25,370 --> 00:31:27,700
They locked me in a cold,
damp side chamber

592
00:31:28,050 --> 00:31:29,310
and just left me there.

593
00:31:30,050 --> 00:31:32,080
Only Mei voluntarily stayed with me

594
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:33,940
and took care of me.

595
00:31:37,490 --> 00:31:38,190
Wanyin.

596
00:31:40,970 --> 00:31:42,830
You didn't go through any of that.

597
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:45,120
Don't think about it anymore.

598
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,820
But I've been here for so long,

599
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:50,520
and she's been really good to me.

600
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:51,350
Listen to me,

601
00:31:51,850 --> 00:31:53,910
you inexplicably entered this book,

602
00:31:54,060 --> 00:31:56,120
into a completely unfamiliar world.

603
00:31:57,270 --> 00:31:59,400
Not only did you have to adapt quickly,

604
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:01,010
but you also had to constantly think about

605
00:32:01,010 --> 00:32:02,610
how to deal with Prince Duan,

606
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:04,260
handle the Empress Dowager,

607
00:32:04,610 --> 00:32:06,010
and struggle to survive.

608
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:09,500
You've already been doing very well.

609
00:32:10,910 --> 00:32:12,510
Better than I have, at least.

610
00:32:14,410 --> 00:32:15,140
Without you,

611
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:18,520
I might not have made it this far.

612
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:22,080
I completely understand why you're upset

613
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:23,050
about Mei.

614
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:26,250
But don't ever

615
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:27,840
doubt yourself.

616
00:32:29,170 --> 00:32:30,430
Don't blame yourself.

617
00:32:32,330 --> 00:32:33,050
Alright?

618
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:36,130
Have I really done well enough?

619
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:43,120
But I'm so tired.

620
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:51,920
Let me lean on you for a while.

621
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:56,000
Just a moment,
and I'll be fully recharged.

622
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:04,240
Mei can't stay in the palace anymore.

623
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:07,520
I'll find a chance to send her away.

624
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:32,040
What time is it now?

625
00:33:32,470 --> 00:33:33,330
Just past 9 AM.

626
00:33:36,110 --> 00:33:37,570
How did I sleep for so long?

627
00:33:44,750 --> 00:33:45,610
What about Mei?

628
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:46,930
Has she been fed?

629
00:33:47,990 --> 00:33:48,850
Yes, she has.

630
00:33:50,350 --> 00:33:51,160
Your Highness,

631
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,960
would you like to go check on Mei?

632
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,140
She kept saying this morning

633
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:58,310
that she wanted to see you again.

634
00:34:01,130 --> 00:34:02,790
She also left a letter for you.

635
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:08,300
[To My Lady, personally]

636
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:16,810
[My Lady,
I know you're still angry with me.]

637
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:17,670
[Although you are my mistress,
all these years,]

638
00:34:17,699 --> 00:34:18,420
[I've long regarded you as family—]

639
00:34:18,449 --> 00:34:19,600
[the only person I care about
in this world.]

640
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:21,620
Your Highness,

641
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:23,480
I was ordered to
escort Mei out of the palace,

642
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,080
but she...

643
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:25,090
is gone.

644
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:34,010
My Lady,

645
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:36,340
I know you're still angry with me.

646
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:39,080
Please let me call you "My Lady"
one last time.

647
00:34:40,110 --> 00:34:41,570
From now on in this palace,

648
00:34:42,030 --> 00:34:44,280
everyone will only address you as
"Your Highness,"

649
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:47,340
-and no one will call you "My Lady".
-My Lady, you're up.

650
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:49,730
Although you are my mistress,

651
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,840
all these years,

652
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:53,179
I've long regarded you as family—

653
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:56,690
the only person I care about
in this world.

654
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:59,030
This morning, His Majesty ordered me
to leave the palace.

655
00:34:59,030 --> 00:34:59,760
My Lady!

656
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:00,690
But without you,

657
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:02,150
I'm nothing but

658
00:35:02,150 --> 00:35:04,590
-a wandering soul with nowhere to go.
-My Lady!

659
00:35:04,590 --> 00:35:07,360
Life has no meaning for me anymore.

660
00:35:07,970 --> 00:35:08,850
Before I die,

661
00:35:09,510 --> 00:35:11,770
let this servant do one last thing for you

662
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,670
to repay your kindness.

663
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,940
Whether I succeed or fail,

664
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:18,690
I can only be your maid again

665
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,590
in the next life.

666
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,110
Yu Wanyin,

667
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:53,070
you actually let that maid of yours,

668
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:55,330
-M...
-The Empress Dowager has arrived!

669
00:35:58,670 --> 00:36:00,130
Greetings, Your Majesty.

670
00:36:03,230 --> 00:36:03,960
Consort Shu,

671
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:05,110
are you hurt?

672
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:08,100
Your Majesty, you must stand up for me.

673
00:36:08,170 --> 00:36:10,150
I was just strolling here

674
00:36:10,270 --> 00:36:11,150
when that girl called...

675
00:36:11,150 --> 00:36:11,920
Mei,

676
00:36:11,950 --> 00:36:13,080
yes, Mei,

677
00:36:13,100 --> 00:36:14,190
suddenly rushed out

678
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:16,030
with scissors, trying to stab me,

679
00:36:16,030 --> 00:36:17,540
shouting something about

680
00:36:17,620 --> 00:36:18,950
how I ordered my brother

681
00:36:18,970 --> 00:36:20,540
to harm Noble Consort Yu's father.

682
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:21,950
And just now, Juan

683
00:36:22,030 --> 00:36:23,190
stepped in to protect me

684
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,990
and got this huge cut on her hand.

685
00:36:29,310 --> 00:36:30,690
How dare you, Noble Consort Yu.

686
00:36:30,690 --> 00:36:33,820
Do you have any idea
what kind of disaster you've caused?

687
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:36,590
Noble Consort Yu has become arrogant
from His Majesty's favor

688
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:38,250
and now disregards all rules.

689
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,060
She shall be demoted from

690
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:40,280
Noble Consort to Concubine!

691
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:40,880
Guards,

692
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:42,030
take her to the Cold Palace.

693
00:36:42,030 --> 00:36:42,280
-Yes, Your Majesty!
-Yes, Your Majesty!

694
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:44,010
Await the Emperor's judgment.

695
00:36:44,860 --> 00:36:45,540
Mei!

696
00:36:59,050 --> 00:37:01,370
Zhang San's Diary.

697
00:37:03,770 --> 00:37:05,460
Your Highness, please hurry.

698
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:12,050
Let go of me!

699
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:13,590
Let go of me!

700
00:37:13,690 --> 00:37:14,750
Hold Her Majesty down firmly!

701
00:37:14,750 --> 00:37:16,750
Don't let Her Majesty hurt herself!

702
00:37:16,810 --> 00:37:17,630
Tie her tight!

703
00:37:17,770 --> 00:37:19,130
Let go of me!

704
00:37:19,570 --> 00:37:20,500
It hurts!

705
00:37:21,980 --> 00:37:22,610
Let go of me!

706
00:37:22,610 --> 00:37:23,730
The water is too cold! Change it!

707
00:37:23,730 --> 00:37:24,610
Let go of me!

708
00:37:25,540 --> 00:37:25,980
It hurts...

709
00:37:25,980 --> 00:37:26,580
Hurry, hurry!

710
00:37:26,580 --> 00:37:28,240
-Hold here!
-It's killing me!

711
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,990
Don't just stand there. Come help!

712
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:35,220
-Let go of me!
-Hold her down! Hold her down!

713
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:40,480
-Noble Consort.
-Hurry, hurry!

714
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:41,500
Crown Prince,

715
00:37:42,370 --> 00:37:43,300
don't be afraid.

716
00:37:44,830 --> 00:37:46,060
Hold her down!

717
00:37:57,580 --> 00:37:58,390
Mother,

718
00:37:58,810 --> 00:38:00,360
Mother, are you alright?

719
00:38:00,650 --> 00:38:02,690
When I came to pay my respects yesterday,

720
00:38:02,690 --> 00:38:04,290
weren't you perfectly fine?

721
00:38:04,330 --> 00:38:05,530
How did

722
00:38:05,690 --> 00:38:07,100
your head condition suddenly flare up,

723
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:08,420
making you fall ill?

724
00:38:10,170 --> 00:38:10,970
Could it be...

725
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:12,290
Could it be

726
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:13,580
that you consumed something

727
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:15,590
you shouldn't have?

728
00:38:18,290 --> 00:38:19,330
It was you...

729
00:38:20,690 --> 00:38:21,650
It was you.

730
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,250
-It was you...
-Mother,

731
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:25,690
it was clearly your own carelessness.

732
00:38:25,690 --> 00:38:27,290
How can you blame me?

733
00:38:29,590 --> 00:38:30,560
Mother,

734
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:32,230
do you still remember

735
00:38:32,570 --> 00:38:33,400
saying

736
00:38:33,530 --> 00:38:35,090
the exact same thing to me

737
00:38:35,340 --> 00:38:36,730
back then

738
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:39,130
when I had my miscarriage?

739
00:38:43,740 --> 00:38:44,980
You wicked...

740
00:38:46,130 --> 00:38:46,770
wicked...

741
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:48,500
wicked...

742
00:38:50,410 --> 00:38:51,730
Rest assured, Mother.

743
00:38:52,470 --> 00:38:54,790
If anything happens to you,

744
00:38:55,620 --> 00:38:57,520
I'll help you

745
00:38:58,100 --> 00:39:02,130
protect this empire.

746
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:16,060
Rest assured, Mother.

747
00:39:16,060 --> 00:39:17,640
With me here,

748
00:39:18,250 --> 00:39:20,020
you'll be fine.

749
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:22,080
Rest well and recover.

750
00:39:33,980 --> 00:39:35,190
Crown Prince,

751
00:39:35,420 --> 00:39:36,480
come here quickly.

752
00:39:36,730 --> 00:39:38,590
Your grandmother is calling you.

753
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,720
[Memorial Tablet
of Empress Dowager Li Zhen]

754
00:40:12,810 --> 00:40:13,380
Dan,

755
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:15,940
from now on,

756
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,900
I'm your mother.

757
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:32,720
You must be

758
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:34,100
obedient.
